This product includes software developed as an open-source Model Context
Protocol (MCP) server for shell and SSH operations.

Architecture, security model (tiered authority, append-only hashed audit,
optional OAuth 2.1), and deployment patterns are modeled on a production
MCP gateway ("Vertex") and established operational best practices.

